      <div class="mop">=</div>
      <div class="mres"><div class="lbl">Surplus yours</div><div class="val">$60,000</div></div>
    </div>
    <p>That $60,000 doesn't go to the bank. It goes to the court — and it's waiting for you to claim it.</p>
