    <div class="fear-item"><div class="atag">TRUTH</div><h3>"What if there's no money in my case?"</h3><p>Then I'll tell you — honestly, quickly, and at zero cost to you. I do the research first. If there are no surplus funds or the claim window has closed, I won't waste your time. You'll have real answers either way, for free.</p></div>
